headline: Pinnacle West: Q2 Earnings Snapshot
summary: PHOENIX (AP) — Pinnacle West Capital Corp. PNW) on Wednesday reported profit of $192.6 million in its second quarter. On a per-share basis, the Phoenix-based company said it had net income of $1.58.
